OL,7,FPensioners Michael and Majorie Cawdery
OL,8,Fwere brutally stabbed to death in
OL,9,Ftheir Portadown home in May 2017.
OL,11,FTheir attacker Thomas McEntee - a
OL,12,Fparanoid schizophrenic - who had just
OL,13,Fwalked out of hospital minutes before.
OL,15,FMcEntee, who admitted manslaughter on
OL,16,Fthe grounds of diminished
OL,17,Fresponsibility, was sentenced to a
OL,18,Fminimum of 10 years in prison.
