OL,7,FUTV can reveal the double killer has
OL,8,Fbeen allowed out of jail on what is
OL,9,Fknown as pre-release testing to see if
OL,10,Fhe is suitable for release into the
OL,11,Fcommunity.
OL,13,FThis was on 13 separate occasions
OL,14,Fsince February - four of them on his
OL,15,Fown.
OL,17,FThe problem - relatives of his victims
OL,18,Fweren't told a thing when they should
OL,19,Fhave been.
