OL,3,CKiller freed from jail over dozen
OL,4,Ctimes without victims' family being
OL,5,Cinformed
OL,7,FThat is because they had signed up to
OL,8,Fthe Prisoner Release Victim
OL,9,FInformation Scheme.
OL,11,FAs part of that programme they should
OL,12,Falso have been given opportunity to
OL,13,Fhave their say on the decision to
OL,14,Fallow the double killer out on day
OL,15,Frelease.
OL,17,FCharles Little, who found the bodies
OL,18,Fof his in-laws back in 2017, is
OL,19,Ffurious.
