OL,7,F"You can't put it into words, it is so
OL,8,Ftraumatic, it makes you so angry, so
OL,9,Fangry," he says.
OL,11,FCharles and the rest of the family
OL,12,Ftold the news just a few days ago.
OL,14,FThe Prison Service has apologised,
OL,15,Fblaming it on an administrative error.
OL,17,F"They should have notified us before
OL,18,Fit even started," says Charles.
