OL,7,F"He hasn't been properly approved to
OL,8,Fdo this. So he shouldn't have been out
OL,9,Fat all, because they hadn't done it
OL,10,Fproperly."
OL,12,FTonight - another apology - this time
OL,13,Ffrom Justice Minister Naomi Long.
OL,15,F"This mistake was caused by an
OL,16,Fadministrative error at the time the
OL,17,Ffamily registered, which meant the
OL,18,Fprisoner database system was not
OL,19,Fproperly updated," she says, in a
OL,20,Fstatement to UTV.
