OL,7,F"Michael and Marjorie Cawdery died as
OL,8,Fa result of a vicious attack, and I
OL,9,Fcan fully understand how the family's
OL,10,Fpain and loss has been compounded by
OL,11,Fthis error.
OL,13,F"They have asked to meet with me to
OL,14,Fdiscuss this issue and I will of
OL,15,Fcourse do so as soon as possible.
