OL,7,F"As soon as the Prison Service became
OL,8,Faware of the error, they immediately
OL,9,Fcontacted the family to offer a
OL,10,Fsincere apology and to provide them
OL,11,Fwith all the relevant information. The
OL,12,FPrison Service also notified the
OL,13,FVictims Commissioner and Parole
OL,14,FCommissioner.
OL,16,F"To ensure there can be no repeat of
OL,17,Fthis, a full check of all cases where
OL,18,Fa prisoner is serving a life sentence
OL,19,Fand victims are registered has now
OL,20,Fcommenced.
