OL,7,F"On the wider issue of keeping victims
OL,8,Finformed, the Director General of
OL,9,FPrisons and the Chief Executive of
OL,10,FProbation Board have commissioned an
OL,11,Fexternal review of the current schemes
OL,12,Fto ensure they are trauma informed,
OL,13,Fand victim centred. That review is
OL,14,Ftimely.
OL,16,F"I would reiterate my apology and that
OL,17,Fof the Prison Service for the hurt
OL,18,Fthis has caused.
